--- Quick notes ---
Build from bootstrap to Live images
sh livecd_chroot.sh all 

Update chroot with the latest packages and build Live images
sh livecd_chroot.sh install

If you need to run some specific programs under chroot directory
sh chroot_mount_install.sh
chroot chroot
export HOME=/root
export LC_ALL=C
< run commands inside the new chroot ... >
exit
sh chroot_umount_install.sh

Edit chroot_install_packages.sh to tailor your LiveCD 
